-- Toyota expects to be able to build Prius in North America
-- 
-- Tue Jul 27, 2010 2:46am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/07/27/us-toyota-us-idUSTRE66Q0WR20100727

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - A senior executive of Toyota Motor Corp ( 7203.T ) said on Tuesday he expects the automaker to be able to build Prius gas-electric hybrid cars in North America from the next remodeling. 

 Atsushi Niimi, Toyota executive vice president in charge of production, also said he expects a slow recovery in the U.S. market. (Reporting by  Chang-Ran Kim )